summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing amendatory contracts with the Washington State Interagency Committee for Outdoor Recreation extending the time for completion of the Fauntleroy Park (IAC 70-045A), Thornton Creek Park (IAC 70-017A), Don Armeni extension South (IAC 68-085A), Lake Washington Bicycle Path (IAC 69-076D) and North Beach Park (IAC 70-068A) outdoor recreation and open space projects.
